Repeat: (sl 1, yo) twice, sl 1, k9 [be sure to keep the 2 yo's positioned between the 3 slipp stitches; in the center, there will be a double yo in Color B divided by a slipped stitch of Color A]
sl 1 purl the 1st yo, sl 1, knit the next yo, sl 1, p9  [be sure each Color A slip stitch is slipped omto the right-hand needle before the following yo is worked.)
p9, sl 1, purl the 1st yo, sl 1, knit the next yo, sl 1
